    Finset.card (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1) + 1 := by
  exact_mod_cast h_ind
```

Now we need to show that `Finset.card (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.supportSet V G p ih inst p_1) ≤ (insert s(v, p) (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1)).card`. We use `h_card_union` to rewrite the right-hand side.

```tactics
have h2 : (insert s(v, p) (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1)).card =
    Finset.card (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1) + 1 := by
  exact_mod_cast h_card_union
```

Now we can complete the proof by showing that `LHS ≤ RHS` using `h1` and `h2`.

```tactics
calc
  Finset.card (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.supportSet V G p ih inst p_1) ≤
    Finset.card (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1) + 1 := by
      exact_mod_cast h1
  _ = (insert s(v, p) (@SimpleGraph.LoopWalk.edgeSet V G p ih inst p_1)).card := by
    exact_mod_cast h2
```

